	(text "I2S input\n\nDAC_BCK and DAC_LRCK are shared from \nthe ADC-generated I2S clocks.\nTEENSY_DAC_DATA provides the \nDAC audio data.\nR71-R73 are series damping resistors \nfor the digital audio lines.\n\nPCM5102A configuration\n\nSCK, FMT, DEMP and FLT are tied low\nfor fixed hardware configuration.\nThe PCM5102A uses its internal PLL, \nso no external DAC MCLK is required.\nXSMT is controlled by the Teensy \nand is pulled low by R70, keeping \nthe DAC muted during startup."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 135.128 63.754 0)
		(effects
